# Use Case Diagram (UCD)

**In the scope of this project, there is a direct relationship of _1 to 1_ between Use Cases (UC) and User Stories (US).**

However, be aware, this is a pedagogical simplification. On further projects and curricular units might also exist _1 to N **and/or** N to 1 relationships between US and UC.

**Insert below the Use Case Diagram in a SVG format**

![Use Case Diagram](Domain Model Use Case Diagram.svg)


**For each UC/US, it must be provided evidences of applying main activities of the software development process (requirements, analysis, design, tests and code). Gather those evidences on a separate file for each UC/US and set up a link as suggested below.**

# Use Cases / User Stories
| UC/US  | Description                                                                                                  |                   
|:-------|:-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| US 001 | As a SNS user, I intend to use the application to schedule a vaccine.                                        |
| US 00? | As SNS user, I want to request the vaccination certificate.                                                  |
| US 00? | As a receptionist at a vaccination center, I intend to schedule a vaccine.                                   |
| US 004 | As a receptionist at a vaccination center, I want to register the arrival of a SNS user to take the vaccine. |
| US 00? | As a nurse, I want to request the vaccination certificate.                                                   |
| US 007 | As a nurse, I intend to record adverse reactions of a SNS user.                                              |
| US 008 | As a nurse, I want to record the administration of a vaccine to a SNS user.                                  |
| US 00? | As a nurse, I want to check the list of arrived SNS users.                                                   |
| US 00? | As a nurse, I want to check the user info and health conditions of a SNS use.                                |
| US 00? | As a coordinator, I want to evaluate the performance of the vaccination process.                             |
| US 00? | As a coordinator, I intend to generate reports.                                                              |
| US 00? | As a coordinator, I want to analyze data from other centers.                                                 |
| US 00? | As an administrator, I want to register new vaccination centers.                                             |
| US 012 | As an administrator, I intend to specify a new vaccine type.                                                 |
| US 013 | As an administrator, I intend to specify a new vaccine and its administration process.                       |
| US 0?? | As an administrator, I want to register employees of vaccination centers.                                    |
